</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_577" id="287v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_577_r2l13">Den von weıſſemburg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_577_r2l14"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / als <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> guten <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> von etwıeuıl ſtetten vnd auch vnſer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_577_r2l15"><expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> botten <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> ʒu vlme bey <expan>eınand<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ſınd / alſo haben </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_577_r2l17">vns <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> freẅnde geſagt . daʒ ſıch 
<add><ab facs="#facs_577_r2l16">da </ab></add> vmb dıe ſache <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> dıe ſtett </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_577_r2l18"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Meincʒ . nehſt auf Nıcolaȷ <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> haben . Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_577_r2l19">auch vmb dıe ſache . <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> vormals bey vns vnd ʒu Coſtencʒ / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_577_r2l20">ʒaichnuſſ <expan>begrıffe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeyn / <expan>mang<ex>er</ex>ley</expan> rede vnd <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex>rede</expan> <expan>ergang<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_577_r2l21">Vnd auf das lecʒ ſo haben dıe ſtette der <expan>v<ex>er</ex>eynung</expan> in ſwoben der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_577_r2l22"><expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſtette <expan>botte<ex>n</ex></expan> / ein ſchrıft <expan>Jr<ex>er</ex></expan> meynung geben / Darnach ſey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_577_r2l23">ein ſchrıft vnd ratſlagung <expan>begrıff<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> . von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_577_r2l24">von Meincʒ ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>beıd<ex>er</ex></expan> ſchrıft . <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_577_r2l25">et <expan>p<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>o<ex>mn</ex>ıa</expan> ut <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_577" id="287v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von Weissemburg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> guten
                                <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> von etwievil stetten und auch unser
                                <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> botten
                            <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> zu Ulme
                            bey<expan>einand<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> sind, also haben uns
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> frewnde gesagt, daz sich <add>da</add> umb
                        die sache, <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> die stett
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Meincz nehst auf <app><note><q type="date">Nicolai</q>06.12.1422</note></app>
<expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> haben, und auch umb die sache,
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> vormals bey uns und zu Costencz
                        zaichnuss <expan>begriffe<ex>n</ex></expan> seyn,
                            <expan>mang<ex>er</ex>ley</expan> rede und
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex>rede</expan>
<expan>ergang<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>; und auf das lecz so haben die stette der
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>eynung</expan> in Swoben der
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> stette <expan>botte<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        ein schrift <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> meynung geben, darnach sey ein
                        schrift und ratslagung <expan>begriff<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Meincz sache
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>; <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>beid<ex>er</ex></expan> schrift <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                        et <expan>p<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>o<ex>mn</ex>ia</expan> ut <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
